## Configuration Checklist
- [ ] Confirm deployment target: self-hosted, third-party API, or consumer
- [ ] For self-hosted: confirm model weights are loaded and endpoint is healthy
- [ ] For sensitive data: confirm no logging or telemetry is enabled
- [ ] Select correct model variant: Scout for massive context, Maverick for general tasks
- [ ] For fine-tuned models: confirm the correct checkpoint is loaded
- [ ] Third-party API: confirm API key and endpoint URL are configured
